edu.snu.onyx.runtime.master.scheduler

Class SingleJobTaskGroupQueue

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.snu.onyx.runtime.master.scheduler.SingleJobTaskGroupQueue
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    PendingTaskGroupQueue

    @ThreadSafe
public final class SingleJobTaskGroupQueue
extends Object
implements PendingTaskGroupQueue
    Keep tracks of all pending task groups. This class provides two-level queue scheduling by prioritizing TaskGroups of certain stages to be scheduled first. Stages that are mutually independent alternate turns in scheduling each of their TaskGroups. This PQ assumes that stages/task groups of higher priorities are never enqueued without first removing those of lower priorities (which is how Scheduler behaves) for simplicity.
